    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under CPB conditions. RH < 1 criterion satisfied across all five operating points. Validation evidence from Morrison et al. (2023) CPB experiments and Hariharan et al. (2011) LVAD benchmark collectively support model credibility. Decision: Accepted for intended use in 510(k) submission to support worst-case hemolysis identification.",
